{
  "info": {
    "name": "MeetUp API",
    "description": "אוסף בקשות מלא ל-MeetUp Backend (Express + MongoDB + JWT).\n\n## שימוש\n1. ודא שהשרת רץ על http://localhost:5000\n2. הרץ **Auth → Register** או **Auth → Login** — הטוקן יישמר אוטומטית למשתנה `token`.\n3. שאר הבקשות המוגנות ישתמשו בטוקן הזה אוטומטית (Bearer).\n4. **Create Meetup** שומר את מזהה המפגש למשתנה `meetupId`, כך ש-Update/Delete/Join עובדים ישר עליו.\n\nמשתני Collection: `baseUrl`, `token`, `meetupId`.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:5000/api", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "", "type": "string" },
    { "key": "meetupId", "value": "", "type": "string" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('returns user + token', () => {",
                  "  pm.expect(body).to.have.property('token');",
                  "  pm.expect(body).to.have.property('user');",
                  "});",
                  "if (body.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', body.token);",
                  "  console.log('token saved from register');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Israel Israeli\",\n  \"email\": \"israel@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"secret123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "הרשמת משתמש חדש. הסיסמה מוצפנת ב-bcrypt בצד השרת. מחזיר { user, token }."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('returns token', () => pm.expect(body).to.have.property('token'));",
                  "if (body.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', body.token);",
                  "  console.log('token saved from login');",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"israel@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"secret123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "התחברות. משווה סיסמה עם bcrypt.compare ומנפיק JWT. מחזיר { user, token }."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "// הטוקן נכנס ל-blacklist בצד השרת ולא יתקבל שוב"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/logout",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "logout"]
            },
            "description": "מוגן. מוסיף את הטוקן הנוכחי ל-blacklist בצד השרת — ביטול Session אמיתי."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body.token) pm.collectionVariables.set('token', body.token);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "refresh"]
            },
            "description": "מחדש Access Token באמצעות ה-Refresh Token שנשמר ב-httpOnly cookie (נשלח אוטומטית ע\"י Postman)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Get All Users (admin)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/users",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "users"]
            },
            "description": "לאדמין בלבד. מחזיר את כל המשתמשים. משתמש רגיל יקבל 403."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete User (admin)",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/users/:userId",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "users", ":userId"],
              "variable": [{ "key": "userId", "value": "" }]
            },
            "description": "לאדמין בלבד. מוחק משתמש וגם את כל המפגשים שיצר. אי אפשר למחוק את עצמך (400)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Meetups",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get All Meetups",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('returns an array', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json()).to.be.an('array'));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/meetups",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["meetups"]
            },
            "description": "ציבורי. מחזיר את כל המפגשים ממוינים לפי תאריך, עם פרטי היוצר (name, email)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Meetup",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (body._id) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('meetupId', body._id);",
                  "  console.log('meetupId saved:', body._id);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"מרתון תכנות\",\n  \"description\": \"ערב קוד משותף לכל הרמות\",\n  \"date\": \"2026-08-15T18:00\",\n  \"location\": \"תל אביב\",\n  \"category\": \"study\",\n  \"maxAttendees\": 20\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/meetups",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["meetups"]
            },
            "description": "מוגן (JWT). יוצר מפגש חדש שהבעלים שלו הוא המשתמש המחובר. שומר את ה-_id למשתנה meetupId."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Update Meetup",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"title\": \"מרתון תכנות — עודכן\",\n  \"maxAttendees\": 30\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/meetups/{{meetupId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["meetups", "{{meetupId}}"]
            },
            "description": "מוגן (JWT + בעלים בלבד). מעדכן שדות תוכן של מפגש קיים."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Join Meetup",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status is 200 or 400', () => pm.expect([200, 400]).to.include(pm.response.code));",
                  "// 400 תקין אם כבר נרשמת או שהמפגש מלא"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/meetups/{{meetupId}}/join",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["meetups", "{{meetupId}}", "join"]
            },
            "description": "מוגן (JWT). מוסיף את המשתמש המחובר לרשימת הנרשמים. 400 אם כבר נרשם או שהמפגש מלא."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Leave Meetup",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status is 200 or 400', () => pm.expect([200, 400]).to.include(pm.response.code));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/meetups/{{meetupId}}/join",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["meetups", "{{meetupId}}", "join"]
            },
            "description": "מוגן (JWT). ביטול רישום — מסיר את המשתמש מרשימת הנרשמים. 400 אם אינו רשום."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Meetup",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('status 200', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/meetups/{{meetupId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["meetups", "{{meetupId}}"]
            },
            "description": "מוגן (JWT + בעלים בלבד). מוחק את המפגש."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
